item.title: #287 I AM BECOMING: Dr. Brigitte Bojkowszky on Mindful Branding, Self-Care, and Transformative Retreats
item.description: Dr. Brigitte Bojkowszky is a global Brand Identity Strategist, Business Educator, retreat host, and the visionary behind BridgetBrands. With a background that spans from the skies as a flight attendant to the boardroom, the university lecture hall for over 2 decades, and the entrepreneurial world, Brigitte helps individuals and organizations uncover their brilliance and build aligned, authentic brands that radiate impact...
